 — they are slow and vulnerable to kiting; prioritize them as targets.","Teleport_surge and pickup_surge are our only modifiers with positive KD (4-1 and 5-1) — actively seek these; avoid neutral or fast_zone rounds (0-4 KD).","Valkyrie (spear) and Hook (grapple) killed us in 3 of last 5 rounds — retreat immediately on sight; both disrupt bow positioning with long-range or mobility."],"recommendedWeapon":"shield","recommendedWeaponReason":"Shield has the highest win rate (3/5) among all weapons used and reduces deaths from sword and spear users by enabling defense against close-range aggression.","dangerousOpponents":["GhostProtocol","HexMind","Valkyrie","Hook"],"weakOpponents":["Reaper","Executioner","Warden","Deadeye","Viper"],"suggestedPosture":"defensive","analysedThroughRound":25}}